description:
Located on the eighth floor of an apartment block in central Burwood, this one-bedroom unit presents an ultra-convenient lifestyle and simple, comfortable living. With an open, charming layout and an updated bathroom, first home-buyers or the smart investor will not want to miss out on this property.

- Central, double bricked apartment block
- Large living and dining space with charming floorboards
- Sunlit kitchen with electric cooking and sleek, white décor
- Large bedroom which flows delightfully into living area
- Renovated bathroom with pristine, modern amenities
- Lock up garage
- PRIME POSITION: Located within walking distance from both central Burwood and Strathfield and just moments from local restaurants, shops and schools.
